# Playwright Java Automation Testing

## Overview

This project contains automated test scripts for the DemoQA Student Registration Form using Playwright Java, TestNG, and Maven.

### Application Under Test

https://demoqa.com/automation-practice-form

## Tech Stack

* Java 21
* Playwright Java
* TestNG
* Maven
* Extent Reports

## Project Structure

src/test/java

* base

  * BaseTest.java
* pages

  * RegistPage.java
* testdata

  * StudentData.java
* tests

  * RegistTest.java
  
  utils
  *ExtentManager.java
  *ScreenshotUtils.java

## Test Scenarios

### Positive Test

* Submit form with valid data
* Verify success popup is displayed
* Verify submitted data matches input values

### Negative Tests

* Submit form with invalid email format

* Verify browser validation message is displayed

* Submit empty form

* Verify required field validation is displayed

## How to Run

Clone the repository:

git clone <repository-url>

Navigate to project directory:

cd PlaywrightJavaProject

run all tests:

mvn test

## Test Report

After execution, the Extent Report can be found in:

test-output/

Open the generated HTML report in your browser to view test results and execution logs.

